strings.name: Incontro Mappatori Romani
strings.description: Improve OpenStreetMap in the Rome area
strings.extendedDescription: We aim to be a resource for people to discuss and share knowledge on utilizing free geographic data sets especially OpenStreetMap, and Open geo-spatial software that manages, edits, and displays geographic data, and advocate for its use in Lazio.
